---
title: Lemon Pepper Salmon with Dill & Parsley Potato Salad
description: Brighten your day with a summertime classic, perfect for a day spent around a delicious meal. Salmon is sure to bring a
sunny feel with zesty pepper spices to add a kick of flavour. Cool off by taking a bite of creamy and herby potato salad.
